description: Attention investors, developers & sweat-equity seekers, presented for the first time in 50 years, this semi-detached single family can be your winter project! Located on a great side street in the heart of Southie, this property is ready for an extensive transformation that will be worth the effort.  A covered entrance leads to a front living room anchored by bay windows. The eat-in kitchen has a spacious footprint with an easily flow to the large rear deck. There's also a 1/2 bath on this level. The 2nd level hosts a skylight, full bath & 3 bedrooms. Vinyl siding, 2022 rubber roof & 2021 hot water heater complete this semi-detached home. A commuter's dream, conveniently located very close to several bus stops, 2 T-Stations, tons of dining + shopping, Carson Beach, highways and all that the vibrant Southie lifestyle has to offer. The property is being sold "AS-IS" & buyers shall do their own due diligence to verify all information.
